data.description: New Lower Price...Location, Convenience and Charm is what you will find in this updated 3 bedroom 1 bath home. Step inside and you'll feel right at home in the inviting living room with hardwood floors. Just a few steps away is the kitchen with modern finishes and the cheery breakfast nook. Ever had a princess tub, that's what you'll find in this gleaming bath. Check out the oversized den perfect for dining room, game room or just a room of your choice. How about the fenced, level backyard with raised garden bed and storage building that's great for entertaining. There's so much to love about this move in ready home! It's waiting for YOU!
